---
import LegalLayout from '@/layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout
  locale="en"
  title="Terms of Service"
  effectiveDate="Effective May 17, 2026"
  tldr={[
    'You own your entries and content.',
    'Use DailyMood in ways that don\'t harm others or break the law.',
    'Pro is an auto-renewing subscription — cancel anytime.',
    'DailyMood is not a medical service. For urgent mental-health concerns, contact a professional.',
  ]}
>
  <h2>1. Acceptance</h2>
  <p>
    By signing up and using DailyMood, you accept these terms. If you don't
    agree with them, please don't use the service.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Your account</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>You must be <strong>at least 13 years old</strong> to create an account.</li>
    <li>Provide accurate, current information.</li>
    <li>You're responsible for keeping your password safe.</li>
    <li>One person per account — no account sharing.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Acceptable use</h2>
  <p>You agree not to use DailyMood to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Violate Thai law or other people's rights</li>
    <li>Post illegal content, hate speech, or content that harms others</li>
    <li>Reverse-engineer, scrape, or attempt to break the system</li>
    <li>Abuse our AI for purposes outside the app (e.g. using us as a free AI service)</li>
    <li>Create fake accounts or impersonate others</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We reserve the right to suspend accounts that violate these terms.</p>

  <h2>4. Pro subscription</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Pro is billed monthly (฿99/mo) or yearly (฿949/yr) via Stripe — it
      auto-renews.
    </li>
    <li>
      Cancel anytime from your Subscription page in Profile. You keep Pro
      features until the end of your current billing period.
    </li>
    <li>Prices may change — we'll give at least 30 days' notice.</li>
    <li>
      No refunds for periods already used, except where required by Thai law.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Your content</h2>
  <p>
    Your mood entries, notes, and photos in DailyMood
    <strong>belong to you</strong>. We don't claim ownership. You grant us
    only the minimum rights needed to display and process your data so the
    app can work.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Disclaimers</h2>
  <p>
    DailyMood is provided <strong>"as is"</strong>. We do our best to keep
    the service reliable but can't guarantee it'll be free of bugs or
    outages.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Important:</strong> DailyMood is not a medical, psychiatric, or
    therapy service. AI insights and any in-app content are observational
    only, not medical advice. If you're experiencing a serious mental-health
    issue, please contact a qualified professional. In Thailand, the Mental
    Health Hotline is 1323.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Changes and termination</h2>
  <p>
    We may update these terms over time. For significant changes, we'll
    notify you by email or in-app at least 30 days in advance. You can
    delete your account anytime from Settings.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about these terms? Reach us at
    <a href="mailto:hello@dailymood.me">hello@dailymood.me</a>.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
